        "From an HR perspective, this employee would benefit most from {\"early ownership and stretch responsibilities\" if a_score >= 75 else \"structured guidance with regular feedback touchpoints\" if a_score >= 55 else \"clear reassurance, simplified expectations, and focused support\"}. Aligning support mechanisms with this psychological profile will significantly enhance engagement, performance, and long-term retention.\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "\n",
        "# ===============================\n",
